      Press release
    </span>
  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Mark White becomes UK’s second Groceries Code Adjudicator
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Mark White has been appointed the UK's second Groceries Code Adjudicator (GCA). </p>

  </div>
</div>

